The paper deals with image processing and compression techniques, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of wavelets and Fourier transforms also suggests a potential fit for information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.MM). Finally, the focus on storage and computation efficiency could also place this paper in the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SI).
